item.title: Does anyone have a nice Highscores
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

-Nothing:

@Matt: You pretty much want to be spoonfed

This pretty much covers it. This community is typically welcoming to newcomers but once we realise that you want everything done for you it’s game over.
If you want to improve your stature in this community then start adding value to it. Do that by first educating yourself and, once educated sufficiently, creating value.
Programming isn’t for everyone, so if you can’t get past the educating-yourself stage then call it quits and just play someone else’s server.
